        {
            "_id": "16ZFULnotAOQsWlX",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Bloody Wail",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The warshard wight cries out in an unearthly shriek. Living creatures within 50 feet must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:23] save. The warshard wight can't make another bloody wail for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected and becomes temporarily immune for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature bleeds from their ears and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature bleeds from their ears and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, and the creature takes a –2 status penalty to saving throws against drain life.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "auditory",
                        "divine"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "s11JB7gJU2rA1XmT",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Drain Life",
            "sort": 700000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When the warshard wight damages a living creature with a melee Strike using an unarmed attack or its bound weapon, the warshard wight gains 5 temporary Hit Points and the creature must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:20] save or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1}. Further damage dealt by the warshard wight increases the drained condition value by 1 on a failed save, to a maximum of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 4}.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
